#: server/activities/tens_complement_find/ActivityEditor.qml:17
msgctxt "ActivityEditor|"
msgid ""
"Do not add too many \"Extra cards\"! Each sublevel must not have more than 6 "
"cards, and there is already 1 card per addition, or 2 cards per addition if "
"\"Find both numbers\" is selected."
msgstr ""
"Ne dodajajte preveč \"dodatnih kart\"! Vsaka podraven ne sme imeti več kot 6 "
"kart, in že je 1 karta na seštevanje oziroma 2 karti na seštevanje, če je "
"izbrana možnost \"Poišči obe števili\"."

#: server/activities/tens_complement_find/ActivityEditor.qml:19
msgctxt "ActivityEditor|"
msgid ""
"If \"Random questions\" is not selected, \"First operands\" of each sublevel "
"must contain 1, 2 or 3 numbers between 1 and 9. There is one addition for "
"each \"First operand\" number."
msgstr ""
"Če možnost \"Naključna vprašanja\" niso izbrana, morajo \"Prvi operandi\" "
"vsake podravni vsebovati 1, 2 ali 3 številke med 1 in 9. Za vsako številko "
"\"Prvega operanda\" je eno seštevanje."

